# Water dimer, occ-RI-K exchange (Manzer et al, JCP 143, 024113 (2015)).
# Same RI-HF as water_dimer_rihf but with the occ-RI-K algorithm; the
# total energy matches RI-K to ~1e-9 while the virtual orbitals differ.
System water_dimer.xyz
Method HF
Basis aug-cc-pVDZ
JKMethod RI
FittingBasis aug-cc-pVDZ-JK
OccRIK true
Direct false
IntegralThresh 1e-14



Logfile water_dimer_rihf_occk.log
SaveChk water_dimer_rihf_occk.chk
BasisRotate false
